data.description: Welcome to 205 Shaw Ct, Fredericksburg, VA 22405, where you'll find an exceptional opportunity to immerse yourself in the tranquil charm of riverfront living. This beautiful property enjoys a prime location, just a short 5-minute drive from Downtown Fredericksburg and a mere mile from the VRE train station.  Step inside to discover a generously spacious gourmet kitchen, a haven for culinary enthusiasts. The kitchen truly shines with its pristine white cabinets, recessed lighting, and a substantial central island, perfect for hosting and entertaining guests. The living room offers a warm and inviting ambiance with its cozy fireplace, and a ceiling fan, ensuring a well-lit and comfortable setting.  With three roomy bedrooms, including a luxurious master bathroom, and a capacious 2-car garage, there's ample room for the whole family to enjoy.  Buyers will especially appreciate the rare gem that this turnkey 3-level townhome represents. It showcases an inviting open floor plan, newly adorned floors, a rear deck overlooking the neighborhood playground, and a spacious garage.  Upstairs, you'll discover three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, with the master bathroom boasting double sinks, a deep soaking tub, and a separate shower. In total, this home features three bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, making it an ideal place to call your own.
